    "content": "{\n  \"narration\": \"You step inside the Harrow's Hollow General Store, the door swinging shut behind you with a gentle chime. The interior is bright in the morning light, shelves neatly organized with everything a traveler—or hero—might need. Your eyes quickly take in the inventory: \\n\\n- Adventurer's packs complete with essentials for journeys unknown\\n- Lanterns (hooded and bullseye) in neat rows with spare flasks of oil\\n- Sturdy ropes, iron spikes, and flint & steel for the rough road ahead\\n- Dried provisions—salted meats, crusty bread, and small wheels of hard cheese\\n- Simple weapons: a few well-balanced daggers, a short sword, even a battered but serviceable wooden shield\\n- Cured leather pouches and satchels for carrying coin or keepsakes\\n\\nOne shelf displays a hand-drawn map of local trails, and beside the ledger rests a tarnished bronze key marked with a faded raven sigil. The air smells pleasantly of leather, wax, and the faintest hint of dried thyme. \\n\\nElder Mirna looks up from her ledger, her expression warm. \\\"Good morning, Norn. I trust you're finding the village more welcoming now that the shadows have lifted? If you require supplies, just say the word—adventurer's packs are one gold, rations five silver for ten days, and good lanterns five gold. Not a potion to be had, mind you—apologies, our herbalist moved north last winter.\\\"\\n\\nShe leans in a little, lowering her voice. \\\"As for news—folk still talk of flickering lights by the old keep, and someone left a strange bone charm on my stoop last night. There's a reward posted for the lost sheep as well, if your heroics run to livestock.\\\"\\n\\nShe pauses, appraising you with a knowing gaze. \\\"You've earned your reward, and the gratitude of every soul here. If you want to see it, or hear about opportunities for one with your skills, just ask.\\\"\\n\\nIs there a particular item you're interested in, or do you have questions for Elder Mirna about the key, the map, or any of the rumors swirling through Harrow's Hollow?\",\n  \"actions\": []\n}"
