nt to hear the story behind it, just say the word. And if you're curious about your reward, well—heroes shouldn't leave empty-handed.\\\"\",\n  \"actions\": [\n    {\n      \"action\": \"updateTime\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"timeEstimate\": 5\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"action\": \"updatePlot\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"plotPointId\": \"PP005\",\n        \"newStatus\": \"in progress\",\n        \"plotImpact\": \"Norn inquires after local rumors and carefully examines the store's rare trinkets, prompting Elder Mirna to share both warnings and hopeful tales, and deepening the sense of ongoing mystery and opportunity in Harrow's Hollow.\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"
